        "text": "你要吃，卻吃不飽； 因你的腹中常有疾病。 你要懷孕，卻不能生下來； 你生下來的， 我都要交給刀劍。"
      },
      "cunp": {
        "version_id": "CUNP",
        "version_name": "和合本新標點（神版）",
        "lang": "cht",
        "text": "你要吃，卻吃不飽； 你的虛弱必顯在你中間。 你必挪去，卻不得救護； 所救護的，我必交給刀劍。"
      },
      "nasb": {
        "version_id": "NASB",
        "version_name": "New American Standard Bible",
        "lang": "en",
        "text": "You will eat, but you will not be satisfied, And your vileness will be in your midst. You will try to remove for safekeeping, But you will not preserve anything, And what you do preserve I will give to the sword."
      },
      "niv": {
        "version_id": "NIV",
        "version_name": "New International Version",
        "lang": "en",
        "text": "You will eat but not be satisfied; your stomach will still be empty. You will store up but save nothing, because what you save I will give to the sword."
      },
      "nlt": {
        "version_id": "NLT",
        "version_name": "New Living Translation",
        "lang": "en",
        "text": "You will eat but never have enough. Your hunger pangs and emptiness will remain. And though you try to save your money, it will come to nothing in the end. You will save a little, but I will give it to those who conquer you."
      }
